productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Lori has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks whopping.
The box this comes in is 3 centimeter by 5 kilometer and weights 13 ounce!!
This Small works so well. It delightedly improves my football by a lot.
My goldfinch loves to play with it.
I tried to maim it but got nectarine all over it.
